title: Cal Smart Caribbean-Inspired Pork Chops with Jewelled Couscous and Mango Hot Sauce
description: Bring a taste of the Caribbean islands to your dinner table tonight! Succulent jerk-seasoned pork chops and fluffy jewelled couscous is accompanied by a sweet and tangy mango hot sauce that will knock your socks off!
